channel.title: How to put my server online!
channel.description:
Hello again. I was wondering how to put my RSPS online. I set it all up with hamachi, no-ip and utorrent; But it only lets ME log in when i set the server as my hamachi server. Please help as i'm getting frustrated because this is very confusing for me. I would really appreciate it.
If there's any additional information i could possibly add, just let me know and I am willing to give out my TV (TeamViewer) so somebody can help me.
-Thanks!

item.dc:creator: @ultimatepkvillage ultimatepkvillage
item.description:
@ultimatepkvillage wrote:

no-ip only works if you portforward through your router, you probably didn’t since your using hamachi so you really don’t even need to use no-ip unless your gonna portforward. To get your server online for others have you made a network group and had them join and also have them connect to your hamachi ip?
